20to%20focus%20on.%20It's%20a%20tough%20job%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20playing%20the%20role%20of%20opener%20in%20the%20team%2C%20Rohit%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20like%20to%20be%20put%20in%20a%20place%20where%20its%20slightly%20difficult%20conditions%20and%20situations.%20I%20always%20wanted%20to%20be%20challenged%20all%20the%20time.%20The%20hardest%20part%20is%20to%20start%20because%20you%20don't%20know%20what%20the%20outcome%20will%20be.%20Confidence%20is%20something%20that%20you%20can't%20take%20from%20anywhere%20it%20needs%20to%20come%20from%20within%20and%20that%20starts%20how%20I%20train%20before%20the%20game.%20If%20I%20want%20to%20play%20a%20certain%20shot%20in%20the%20first%20over%2C%20I%20have%20to%20practice%20that.%20I%20have%20to%20master%20that%20shot%20to%20gain%20confidence.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20ongoing%20five-match%20Test%20series%20between%20India%20and%20England%2C%20the%20hosts%20suffered%20their%20fourth%20home%20Test%20defeat%20in%20a%20decade%20in%20Hyderabad%2C%20as%20visitors%20overwhelmed%20the%20Rohit-led%20side%20thanks%20to%20a%20superb%20196-run%20effort%20by%20Ollie%20Pope%20and%20a%20fantastic%20performance%20on%20Day%204%20by%20debutant%20Tom%20Hartley%2C%20who%20picked%20up%20seven%20wickets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20India%20responded%20in%20Vizag%20with%20a%20106-run%20triumph%2C%20levelling%20the%20five-match%20series%20at%201-1.%20With%20the%20five-match%20series%20levelled%20at%201-1%2C%20the%20action%20now%20heads%20to%20Rajkot%20for%20the%20third%20Test%2C%20starting%20February%2015.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707618540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fiff93bsg_rohit-sharma-bcci_625x300_06_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fs