2https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fhelicopter-crash-in-mojave-desert-six-missing%2Famp_articleshow%2F107592982.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hungary%20President%20Resigns%20Over%20Pardon%20To%20Man%20Convicted%20In%20Sex%20Abuse%20Case%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EHungarian%20President%20Katalin%20Novak%2C%20a%20close%20ally%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Viktor%20Orban%2C%20announced%20her%20resignation%20Saturday%20following%20outrage%20over%20a%20pardon%20granted%20to%20a%20man%20implicated%20in%20a%20child%20sexual%20abuse%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20afterwards%20another%20Orban%20supporter%2C%20former%20justice%20minister%20Judit%20Varga%2C%20announced%20she%20was%20withdrawing%20from%20public%20life%20over%20the%20affair.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20announcements%20followed%20growing%20pressure%20from%20opposition%20politicians%20and%20protests%20outside%20the%20presidential%20palace%20Friday%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20resigning%20my%20post%2C%26quot%3B%20said%2046-year-old%20Novak%2C%20acknowledging%20that%20she%20had%20made%20a%20mistake.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20apologise%20to%20those%20who%20I%20hurt%20and%20all%20the%20victims%20who%20may%20have%20had%20the%20impression%20that%20I%20did%20not%20support%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20former%20minister%20for%20family%20policy%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%2C%20I%20was%20and%20I%20will%20remain%20in%20favour%20of%20protecting%20children%20and%20families.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENovak%20became%20the%20first%20woman%20to%20hold%20the%20essentially%20ceremonial%20role%20of%20president%20in%20March%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20controversy%20was%20sparked%20by%20the%20pardon%20granted%20to%20a%20former%20deputy%20director%20of%20a%20children's%20home.%20He%20had%20helped%20to%20cover%20up%20his%20boss's%20sexual%20abuse%20of%20the%20children%20in%20their%20charge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20was%20made%20last%20April%20during%20a%20visit%20by%20Pope%20Francis%20to%20Budapest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20independent%20news%20site%20444%20revealed%20the%20decision%20last%20week%2C%20the%20country's%20opposition%20had%20been%20calling%20for%20Novak's%20resignation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%20evening%20demonstrators%20gathered%20outside%20the%20presidential%20palace%20and%20three%20presidential%20advisers%20quit%20their%20posts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOrban%20must%20'take%20responsibility'%20-%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENovak%2C%20who%20had%20been%20in%20Qatar%20to%20attend%20Hungary's%20match%20against%20Kazakhstan%20at%20the%20World%20Water%20Polo%20Championships%20on%20Friday%2C%20swiftly%20returned%20to%20Budapest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20soon%20as%20her%20plane%20had%20landed%20she%20emerged%20and%20announced%20her%20resignation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20pardon%20granted%20and%20the%20lack%20of%20explanation%20may%20have%20given%20rise%20to%20doubts%20about%20zero%20tolerance%20of%20paedophilia%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20there%20can%20be%20no%20doubt%20on%20this%20subject%26quot%3B%2C%20she%20added%2C%20before%20offering%20her%20apologies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMinutes%20after%20her%20announcement%2C%20another%20ally%20of%20Orban%2C%20Judit%20Varga%2C%20also%20announced%20her%20%26quot%3Bwithdrawal%20from%20public%20life%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20justice%20minister%2C%20a%20post%20she%20quit%20in%20order%20to%20lead%20a%20European%20Parliament%20election%20bid%2C%20she%20had%20approved%20the%20pardon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20renounce%20my%20mandate%20as%20an%20MP%20and%20the%20head%20of%20the%20list%20for%20the%20European%20Parliament%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20on%20Facebook.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20quick%3A%20first%20Novak%2C%20then%20Varga%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Hungarian%20MEP%20Anna%20Donath%2C%20reacting%20to%20the%20news.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20we%20know%20that%20no%20important%2