20Seat%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ERussian%20ambassador%20to%20India%20Denis%20Alipov%20on%20Saturday%20called%20for%20urgent%20reforms%20of%20the%20United%20Nations%20and%20agencies%20under%20it%20while%20making%20a%20strong%20case%20for%20the%20inclusion%20of%20India%20as%20a%20permanent%20member%20of%20the%20UN%20Security%20Council.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20of%20the%20view%20that%20India%20as%20a%20permanent%20member%20of%20the%20Security%20Council%20could%20make%20a%20significant%20contribution%20to%20promoting%20balance%20as%20well%20as%20an%20agenda%20focused%20on%20the%20interests%20of%20the%20world%20majority%2C%20primarily%20the%20countries%20of%20the%20Global%20South%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Russian%20envoy%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20the%20RT%20news%20agency%2C%20the%20Russian%20envoy%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20repeatedly%20indicated%20our%20support%20for%20New%20Delhi's%20candidacy.%20Our%20Indian%20partners%20have%20proven%20themselves%20worthy%20during%20their%20non-permanent%20membership%20in%20the%20UNSC%20in%202021-2022%20and%20have%20successfully%20led%20the%20Council%20twice.%20Their%20G20%20presidency%20was%20also%20a%20clear%20confirmation%20of%20their%20high%20professionalism%20in%20multilateral%20diplomacy%20and%20the%20ability%20to%20find%20consensus%20amid%20growing%20geopolitical%20tensions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-doubt-un-assembly-chief-on-unsc-debate-around-india-4924044%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BNo%20Doubt...%26quot%3B%3A%20UN%20Assembly%20Chief%20On%20Security%20Council%20Debate%20Around%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20alleged%20polarisation%20at%20the%20UN%2C%20the%20envoy%20said%20it%20significantly%20complicates%20the%20expansion%20of%20security%20council%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20West%20already%20has%20an%20overrepresentation%20at%20the%20world%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPolarization%20at%20the%20UN%20significantly%20complicates%20dialogue%20on%20expanding%20the%20Security%20Council%2C%20in%20which%20the%20West%20is%20already%20disproportionately%20'overrepresented'.%20Against%20this%20background%2C%20we%20are%20doubtful%20of%20the%20vigorously%20promoted%20applications%20of%20new%20Western%20candidates%2C%26quot%3B%20Alipov%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20it%20is%20widely%20recognized%20that%20bringing%20the%20composition%20of%20the%20UN%20Security%20Council%20in%20to%20line%20with%20modern%20realities%2C%20bearing%20in%20mind%20the%20well-founded%20aspirations%20of%20India%20and%20other%20reputable%20contenders%20from%20Asia%2C%20Africa%20and%20Latin%20America%20for%20permanent%20membership%2C%20is%20long%20overdue.%20In%20this%20respect%20we%20value%20the%20broadest%20possible%20consensus%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Russian%20ambassador%20to%20India%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECalling%20the%20growing%20trade%20ties%20and%20economic%20and%20bilateral%20relations%20with%20India%20as%20'unprecedented'%2C%20the%20Russian%20envoy%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BOur%20trade%20and%20economic%20cooperation%20has%20reached%20an%20unprecedented%20level.%20Russia%20is%20one%20of%20India's%20four%20main%20trading%20partners.%20We%20maintain%20a%20leading%20position%20in%20the%20supply%20of%20hydrocarbons%20providing%20more%20than%20a%20third%20of%20Indian%20imports.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSupplies%20of%20mineral%20fertilizers%20and%20products%20of%20the%20agricultural%20and%20diamond%20sectors%20are%20growing.%20All%20this%20creates%20a%20favorable%20atmosphere%20for%20our%20mutually%20beneficial%20cooperation%20to%20achieve%20new%20heights%20and%20strengthens%20the%20feeling%20of%20mutual%20trust%20in%20the%20business%20environment%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-mature-respected-member-un-assembly-chief-dennis-francis-on-permanent-unsc-seat-4923740%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BIndia%20Mature%2C%20Respected%20Member%2C%26quot%3B%20UN%20Assembly%20Chief%20On%20Permanent%20UNSC%20Seat%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20and%20Russia%20have%20maintained%20a%20robust%20strategic%20partnership%2C%20rooted%20in%20historical%20ties%20and%20shared%20interests%2C%20over%20decades.%20Central%20to%20this%20relationship%20is%20extensive%20defence%20cooperation%2C%20with%20Russia%20serving%20as%20a%20major%20supplier%20of%20military%20equipment%20to%20India%20and%20both%20nations%20engaging%20in%20joint%20military%20exercises%2C%20co-development%20of%20advanced%20military%20platforms%2C%20and%20technology%20transfers%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Russian%20news%20agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20recently%2C%20energy%20collaboration%20has%20become%20another%20strong%20pillar%20of%20bilateral%20ties.%20The%20Kudankulam%20nuclear%20power%20plant%20(KNPP)%2C%20India's%20largest%2C%20is%20being%20built%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20with%20technical%20assistance%20provided%20by%20Moscow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERussia's%20expertise%20in%20nuclear%20technology%20has%20been%20instrumental%20in%20advancing%20India's%20capabilities%2C%20fostering%20a%20mutually%20beneficial%20partnership%2C%20according%20to%20RT.%20The%20two%20countries%20have%20pledged%20to%20deepen%20their%20nuclear%20cooperation%2C%20recognizing%20its%20strategic%20importance%20for%20energy%20security%20and%20technological%20advancement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%2018%20months%2C%20India%20has%20emerged%20as%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20importers%20of%20Russian%20oil--a%20stand%20New%20Delhi%20has%20had%20to%20defend%20on%20many%20occasions%20from%20accusations%20by%20Western%20media%2C%20and%20even%20some%20political%20leaders%2C%20of%20funding%20'Russia's%20war'%20with%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20th