%20gratitude%20to%20well-wishers%20following%20his%20cancer%20diagnosis%2C%20his%20first%20public%20comment%20since%20Buckingham%20Palace%20announced%20he%20would%20postpone%20some%20engagements%20to%20undergo%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20like%20to%20express%20my%20most%20heartfelt%20thanks%20for%20the%20many%20messages%20of%20support%20and%20good%20wishes%20I%20have%20received%20in%20recent%20days%2C%26quot%3B%20Charles%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20palace%20announced%20on%20Monday%20that%20Charles%2C%2075%2C%20had%20been%20diagnosed%20with%20a%20form%20of%20cancer%2C%20less%20than%2018%20months%20into%20his%20reign.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20all%20those%20who%20have%20been%20affected%20by%20cancer%20will%20know%2C%20such%20kind%20thoughts%20are%20the%20greatest%20comfort%20and%20encouragement%2C%26quot%3B%20Charles%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20king%20said%20it%20was%20heartening%20to%20hear%20how%20his%20diagnosis%20had%20helped%20to%20shine%20a%20light%20on%20the%20organisations%20that%20support%20cancer%20patients%20in%20Britain%20and%20elsewhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENews%20of%20his%20cancer%20came%20after%20Charles%20spent%20three%20nights%20in%20hospital%20last%20month%20where%20he%20underwent%20a%20corrective%20procedure%20for%20a%20benign%20enlarged%20prostate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBuckingham%20Palace%20has%20not%20given%20any%20details%20of%20his%20condition%20other%20than%20to%20say%20it%20was%20not%20prostate%20cancer%2C%20but%20said%20the%20king%20was%20remaining%20%26quot%3Bwholly%20positive%26quot%3B%20and%20looking%20forward%20to%20returning%20to%20public%20duty%20as%20soon%20as%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECharles'%20wife%2C%20Queen%20Camilla%2C%20said%20on%20Thursday%20that%20Charles%20was%20doing%20%26quot%3Bextremely%20well%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20king%20undergoing%20treatment%20and%20Prince%20William's%20wife%20Kate%20recovering%20from%20abdominal%20surgery%2C%