20completely%20rewrite%20the%20history%20of%20key%20periods%20of%20the%20ancient%20world%2C%E2%80%9D%20Robert%20Fowler%2C%20chair%20of%20the%20Herculaneum%20Society%2C%20which%20raises%20awareness%20of%20the%20scrolls%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Ffeatures%2F2024-ai-unlock-ancient-world-secrets%2F%3Futm_content%3Dbusiness%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dtwitter%26utm_campaign%3Dsocialflow-organic%26cmpid%3Dsocialflow-twitter-business%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Etold%20Bloomberg%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20the%20society%20from%20which%20the%20modern%20Western%20world%20is%20descended.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Carbonized%20scroll%20of%20Herculaneum%20papyri.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c7d6386fcb546d2d4e48f7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222436%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Herculaneum%20papyri%20were%20buried%20thousands%20of%20years%20ago%20during%20the%20eruption%20of%20Mt.%20Vesuvius.%3Cp%3ESalvatore%20Laporta%2FAP%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20if%20uncovering%20them%20could%20mark%20a%20pivotal%20point%20in%20human%20history%20then%20their%20burial%20was%20a%20blessing%20in%20disguise.%20Unlike%20%E2%80%9Cvirtually%20every%20ancient%20text%E2%80%9D%20that%20decays%20once%20exposed%20to%20air%2C%20the%20Herculaneum%20papyri%20have%20been%20%E2%80%9Ccarbonized%20by%20the%20heat%20of%20the%20volcanic%20debris%E2%80%9D%20and%20therefore%20preserved%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscrollprize.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20Vesuvius%20Challenge%E2%80%99s%20website%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThree%20tech%20industry%20veterans%20%E2%80%94%20former%20Github%20CEO%20Nat%20Friedman%2C%20founder%20of%20the%20search%20engine%20Cue%2C%20Daniel%20Gross%2C%20and%20computer%20science%20professor%20Brent%20Seales%20%E2%80%94%20launched%20the%20competition%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ein%20March%202023.%20It%20is%20backed%20by%20a%20bevy%20of%20entrepreneurs%2C%20investors%2C%20and%20key%20figures%20in%20the%20tech%20industry.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20year's%20winners%20built%20upon%20work%20already%20underway%20by%20Seales%2C%20who%20used%20X-ray%20tomography%20and%20computer%20vision%20to%20%E2%80%9Cvirtually%20unwrap%E2%80%9D%20the%20scrolls.%C2%A0From%20there%2C%20machine%20learning%20models%20can%20be%20used%20to%20identify%20ink%20and%2C%20ultimately%2C%20decipher%20words.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20passages%20the%20winning%20team%20uncracked%20were%20likely%20written%20by%20the%20Epicurean%20philosopher%20Philodemus%20and%20touch%20on%20%26quot%3Bmusic%2C%20food%2C%20and%20how%20to%20enjoy%20life's%20pleasures%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20a%20post%20by%20Friedman%20on%20X.%20%26quot%3BIn%20the%20closing%20section%2C%20he%20throws%20shade%20at%20unnamed%20ideological%20adversaries%20%E2%80%94%20perhaps%20the%20stoics%3F%20%E2%80%94%20who%20%26quot%3Bhave%20nothing%20to%20say%20about%20pleasure%2C%20either%20in%20general%20or%20in%20particular%2C%26quot%3B%20Friedman%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplatform.twitter.com%2Fwidgets.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ETen%20months%20ago%2C%20we%20launched%20the%20Vesuvius%20Challenge%20to%20solve%20the%20ancient%20problem%20of%20the%20Herculaneum%20Papyri%2C%20a%20library%20of%20scrolls%20that%20were%20flash-fried%20by%20the%20eruption%20of%20Mount%20Vesuvius%20in%2079%20AD.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EToday%20we%20are%20overjoyed%20to%20announce%20that%20our%20crazy%20project%20has%20succeeded.%20After%202000%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Ffihs9ADb48%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Ffihs9ADb48%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%