20hundreds%20of%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20was%20interacting%20with%20the%20Indian%C2%A0Expatriates%20in%20Perth%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20to%20social%20media%20platform%20X%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BAddressed%20the%20Indian%20community%20in%20Perth%20today.%20Grateful%20for%20their%20contribution%20in%20strengthening%20the%20India-Australia%20Dosti.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20the%20event%2C%20S%20Jaishankar%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BDuring%20the%20G20%20virtual%20meet%2C%20the%20biggest%20worry%20was%20how%20will%20India%20cope%20with%20Covid.%20The%20feeling%20was%20India%20didn't%20have%20the%20health%20facilities%2C%20the%20production%2C%20masks%2C%20ventilators.%20We%20started%20Covid%20as%20a%20country%20of%20worry%3B%20we%20ended%20Covid%20as%20a%20country%20of%20contribution.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20same%20India%20not%20just%20looked%20after%20all%20its%20people%20but%20also%20got%20each%201.4%20billion%20people%20vaccinated.%20Hundreds%20of%20countries%20got%20vaccines%2C%20and%20many%20got%20vaccines%20only%20because%20of%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20during%20the%20Covid%20pandemic%2C%20India%20was%20able%20to%20bring%207%20million%20of%20its%20people%20from%20various%20countries%20back%20to%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20further%20said%20that%20government%20officials%20worked%20three%20shifts%20a%20day%20for%20the%20Indian%20community%20abroad%2C%20even%20during%20the%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20happens%20when%20you%20get%20a%20leader%20with%20a%20vision%3F%20I%20can%20tell%20you%20as%20a%20person%20who%20has%20worked%20his%20entire%20life%20in%20the%20government.%20During%20Covid%2C%20people%20worked%20from%20home.%20But%20we%20worked%20three%20shifts%20a%20day%20from%20the%20office%2C%20every%20day.%20We%20could%20do%20this%20because%20we%20were%20motivated.%20There%20was%20a%20drive%2C%20a%20sense%20that%20we%20had%20to%20find%20a%20way%20in%20the%20leadership%20of%20this%20Prime%20Minister%20and%20that%20we%20cannot%20let%20down%20our%20people.%20The%20sense%20that%20we%20have%20a%20community%20abroad%2C%20there%20are%203.5%20crore%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20S%20Jaishnkar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BSo%20that%20sense%20of%20responsibility%2C%20care%20and%20empathy%20has%20been%20another%20hallmark.%20In%20many%20countries%20you%20can%20have%20grand%20visions%20and%20big%20statements%2C%20one%20very%20important%20difference%20in%20India%20is%20that%20the%20biggest%20vision%20has%20become%20the%20smallest%20detail.%20How%20do%20you%20actually%20do%20things%20on%20the%20ground.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20on%20the%20abrogation%20of%20Article%20370%2C%20S%20Jaishankar%20said%20that%20the%20whole%20country%20knew%20that%20was%20the%20%26quot%3Bright%20thing%20to%20do%26quot%3B%20but%20it%20needed%20a%20leader%20with%20'courage%20and%20clarity'%20to%20do%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...We%20have%20gone%20through%20a%20very%20difficult%20situation%20with%20China.%20While%20Covid%20was%20going%20on%2C%20the%20Indian%20military%20was%20deployed%20in%20very%20difficult%20terrain%20in%20large%20numbers%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20challenge.%20One%20very%20critical%20decision%2C%20that%20needed%20to%20be%20taken%2C%20and%20everyone%20knew%20was%20the%20right%20step%2C%20was%20the%20abrogation%20of%20Article%20370%2C%20we%20had%20the%20clarity%2C%20the%20courage.%20Everybody%20knew%20that%20was%20the%20right%20thing%20to%20do%2C%20but%20we%20needed%20a%20leader%20who%20said%2C%20'Yes%20I%20can%20do%20it'%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707594360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22