C%20the%20party%20which%20failed%20to%20lead%20the%20opposition%20INDIA%20block%20would%20be%20responsible%20for%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20Congress%20leader%20also%20thanked%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20for%20conferring%20Bharat%20Ratna%20on%20his%20predecessors%20PV%20Narasimha%20Rao%20and%20Chaudhary%20Charan%20Singh%20and%20said%20they%20deserved%20the%20honours%20for%20their%20outstanding%20contribution%20for%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20to%20reporters%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20a%20public%20meeting%20at%20Garkhal%20in%20Pragwal%20near%20the%20International%20Border%20on%20the%20outskirts%20of%20Jammu%2C%20Mr%20Azad%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20not%20an%20astrologer%20who%20could%20tell%20whether%20they%20(BJP)%20will%20cross%20the%20400-mark%20(in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls).%20If%20it%20happens%2C%20those%20who%20failed%20to%20take%20everyone%20along%20will%20be%20responsible.%20I%20feel%20they%20all%20have%20teamed%20up%20with%20them.%26quot%3B%20He%20was%20responding%20to%20a%20question%20about%20the%20possibility%20of%20the%20BJP%20crossing%20the%20400%20seat-mark%20in%20the%20upcoming%20elections%20and%20National%20Conference%20vice%20president%20Omar%20Abdullah's%20concern%20over%20the%20health%20of%20the%20Indian%20National%20Developmental%20Inclusive%20Alliance%20(INDIA).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20(Omar)%20was%20a%20minister%20in%20the%20(A%20B%20Vajpayee-led)%20BJP%20government.%20He%20might%20have%20remembered%20his%20old%20loyalty%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Azad%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Azad%2C%20a%20former%20chief%20minister%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%2C%20said%20he%20is%20neither%20close%20to%20the%20Congress%20nor%20the%20BJP.%20%26quot%3BLet%20the%20Congress%20speak%20what%20they%20want.%20For%20me%2C%20if%20the%20BJP%20is%20doing%20anything%20wrong%20I%20am%20the%20first%20to%20criticize%20and%20likewise%20if%20Congress%20is%20doing%20anything%20right%2C%20I%20am%20giving%20credit%20to%20them.%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Azad%2C%20who%20floated%20Democratic%20Progressive%20Azad%20Party%20(DPAP)%20in%20September%202022%20after%20resigning%20from%20Congress%2C%20welcomed%20the%20decision%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20to%20award%20Bharat%20Ratna%20to%20Rao%20and%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRao%20brought%20Manmohan%20Singh%20as%20his%20Finance%20minister%20when%20I%20was%20Tourism%20minister%20in%20his%20cabinet.%20His%20liberalization%20policies%20revolutionized%20the%20economy%20to%20keep%20pace%20with%20the%20outside%20world%20which%20was%20moving%20ahead%20of%20us.%20I%20also%20advocated%20liberalization%20policy%20to%20end%20monopoly%20in%20air%20service%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20liberalization%20policy%20introduced%20by%20the%20Rao%20government%20is%20being%20followed%20by%20the%20Modi%20government%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSingh%20was%20the%20tallest%20farmer%20leader%20and%20we%20have%20not%20seen%20anyone%20among%20the%20farming%20community%20to%20come%20closer%20to%20his%20stature.%20Recognizing%20his%20contribution%20for%20the%20country%20will%20boost%20the%20morale%20of%20the%20farming%20community%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Azad%20said%20he%20is%20thankful%20to%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20for%20acknowledging%20the%20work%20of%20the%20two%20leaders%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20the%20nation.%20%26quot%3BIf%20any%20work%20was%20done%20for%20the%20benefit%20of%20the%20country%2C%20it%20should%20be%20appreciated%20and%20if%20the%20present%20government%20is%20doing%20this%2C%20we%20should%20appreciate%20it.%26quot%3B%20On%20the%20prevailing%20situation%20in%20Pakistan%2C%20the%20DPAP%20leader%20said%20the%20free%20and%20fair%20elections%20in%20neighbouring%20countries%20are%20a%20far%20cry%20due%20to%20the%20interference%20of%20the%20Army%20in%20the%20electoral%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSince%20the%20formation%20of%20Pakistan%2C%20we%20(India)%20have%20had%20differences%20with%20it%20and%20Pakistan%20is%20responsible%20for%20the%20tension%20between%20the%20two%20countries.%20Immediately%20after%20independence%2C%20Pakistan%20launched%20an%20attack%20and%20separated%20our%20part%20which%20is%20known%20as%20Pakistan%20occupied%20Kashmir.%20Our%20brothers%20there%20are%20not%20happy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20while%20India%20got%20democracy%20and%20saw%20a%20change%20of%20Prime%20Ministers%20through%20electoral%20exercise%2C%20they%20got%20dictatorship%20and%20the%20army%20is%20running%20the%20governments%20there.%20The%20public%20representatives%20are%20living%20at%20the%20mercy%20of%20the%20Army%20which%20decides%20who%20wins%20or%20loses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20blessed%20that%20our%20army%20or%20anyone%20else%20is%20not%20interfering%20in%20our%20elections%20and%20that%20is%20democracy.%20We%20pray%20that%20such%20an%20atmosphere%20prevails%20there%20as%20well%20for%20the%20benefit%20of%20the%20public%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Parliament%20passing%20the%20Constitution%20(Jammu%20and%20Kashmir)%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20Order%20(Amendment)%20Bill%2C%202024%2C%20adding%20four%20communities%20--%20Gadda%20Brahmin%2C%20Koli%2C%20Paddari%20Tribe%2C%20and%20Pahari%20Ethnic%20Group%20--%20to%20the%20list%20of%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20Azad%20said%20it%20was%20a%20longstanding%20demand%20of%20the%20people%20and%20%26quot%3Bwe%20have%20always%20supported%20them%20on%20the%20condition%20that%20the%20reservation%20enjoyed%20by%20Gujjars%20and%20Bakerwals%20remains%20untouched.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707590820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-05%2F2hoo62b4_ghulam-nabi-azad-ani_625x300_24_May_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%