%20the%20age%20of%2011.%20She%20had%20scolded%20Pinku%20over%20playing%20too%20much%20and%2C%20in%20a%20fit%20of%20rage%2C%20he%20had%20run%20away%20from%20their%20Delhi%20home%20in%202002.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20Bhanumati%20and%20her%20husband%2C%20Ratipal%20Singh%2C%20got%20information%20that%20an%20ascetic%20was%20visiting%20Ratipal's%20native%20village%2C%20Kharauli%20in%20Amethi%2C%20and%20he%20bore%20the%20same%20scar%20as%20Pinku.%20His%20relatives%20-%20including%20his%20sister%2C%20who%20stays%20in%20the%20village%20-%20asked%20Ratipal%20and%20Bhanumati%20to%20rush%20to%20Kharauli%20and%2C%20when%20they%20reached%20there%20on%20January%2027%2C%20the%20ascetic%20told%20them%20that%20he%20was%20indeed%20their%20son.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20video%20of%20the%20ascetic%20seeking%20alms%20from%20Bhanumati%2C%20singing%20folk%20songs%20about%20a%20king%20who%20left%20his%20kingdom%20to%20become%20a%20monk%2C%20went%20viral.%20In%20the%20video%2C%20tears%20of%20joy%20can%20be%20seen%20streaming%20down%20Bhanumati's%20cheek.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20twist%20followed%2C%20with%20a%20bigger%20one%20yet%20to%20come.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPinku%20told%20them%20that%20he%20had%20taken%20%3Cem%3Esanyaas%3C%2Fem%3E%20(renounced%20earthly%20pleasures)%20and%20had%20to%20return%20to%20his%20monastery%2C%20Parasnath%20Math%2C%20in%20Jharkhand.%20He%20said%20his%20guru%20had%20told%20him%20his%20initiation%20would%20be%20complete%20only%20after%20he%20visited%20Ayodhya%20and%20then%20took%20alms%20from%20his%20family%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20parents%20initially%20refused%20to%20let%20Pinku%20go%20but%2C%20realising%20that%20his%20heart%20was%20set%20on%20following%20the%20path%20he%20was%20on%2C%20eventually%20gave%20in.%20Villagers%20came%20together%20to%20contribute%2013%20quintals%20of%20foodgrain%20as%20alms%20and%20Ratipal's%20sister%20also%20gave%20him%20Rs%2011%2C000.%20Ratipal%20bought%20Pinku%20a%20phone%20and%20asked%20him%20to%20keep%20in%20touch.%20Pinku%20left%20the%20village%20on%20February%201.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPolice%20Complaint%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20Pinku%20left%2C%20he%20began%20calling%20Ratipal%20and%20said%20he%20wanted%20to%20return%20to%20them%2C%20but%20claimed%20that%20people%20at%20the%20monastery%20had%20told%20him%20he%20couldn't%20do%20so%20until%20he%20had%20given%20them%20Rs%2010%20lakh.%20This%2C%20he%20told%20Ratipal%2C%20was%20the%20price%20a%20monk%20had%20to%20pay%20to%20return%20to%20family%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDesperate%20to%20have%20his%20son%20back%20with%20the%20family%2C%20Ratipal%20sold%20his%20land%20in%20the%20village%20for%20Rs%2011.2%20lakh%20and%20then%20told%20Pinku%20that%20he%20would%20come%20to%20Jharkhand%20to%20give%20the%20money%20to%20the%20monastery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20police%20official%2C%20Pinku%20gave%20several%20reasons%20-%20none%20very%20believable%20-%20for%20why%20Ratipal%20should%20not%20come%20to%20the%20monastery.%20He%20also%20began%20insisting%20that%20Ratipal%20send%20him%20the%20money%20via%20bank%20transfer%20or%20using%20a%20UPI%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20made%20Ratipal%20suspicious%20and%20he%20began%20making%20enquiries%2C%20only%20to%20find%20that%20there%20was%20no%20Hindu%20monastery%20in%20Jharkhand%20by%20the%20name%20of%20Parasnath%20Math.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20Saturday%2C%20Ratipal%20filed%20a%20complaint%20in%20Jais%20police%20station%20(in%20Amethi%20district)%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Tiloi%20Circle%20Officer%20Ajay%20Kumar%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20then%20found%20that%20the%20man%20masquerading%20as%20Pinku%20was%20actually%20someone%20called%20Nafees%20from%20Gonda%20village%2C%20who%20was%20trying%20to%20scam%20the%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFamily%20Business%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20official%20said%20further%20enquiries%20revealed%20that%20Nafees'%20brother%2C%20Rashid%2C%20had%20posed%20as%20an%20ascetic%20and%20cheated%20a%20family%20of%20lakhs%20using%20nearly%20the%20same%20playbook%20in%20July%202021.%20Ravi%2C%20the%20son%20of%20a%20man%20named%20Budhiram%20Vishwakarma%20had%20gone%20missing%20from%20Sahaspura%20village%2014%20years%20ago%20and%20Rashid%20had%20reached%20the%20village%20pretending%20to%20be%20an%20ascetic.%20He%20claimed%20he%20was%20Ravi%20and%20asked%20Budhiram's%20wife%20for%20alms.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20family%20made%20Rashid%20stay%20with%20them%20thinking%20he%20was%20Ravi%20and%20then%20he%20disappeared%20with%20lakhs%20in%20cash.%20His%20true%20identity%20came%20to%20the%20fore%20when%20he%20was%20arrested%20later.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20days%20before%20Rashid%20reached%20Sahaspura%20village%2C%20a%20relative%20of%20Nafees%20showed%20up%20at%20the%20house%20of%20Kallu%20Rajbhar%20in%20Varanasi's%20Hajipur%20village.%20In%20an%20ascetic's%20attire%2C%20he%20pretended%20to%20be%20Kallu's%20son%2C%20who%20had%20gone%20missing%2015%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Investigation%20On'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECircle%20Officer%20Ajay%20Kumar%20Singh%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BRatipal%20Singh%20has%20complained%20that%20his%20family%20gave%20a%20person%20grain%20after%20being%20told%20a%20man%20dressed%20as%20an%20ascetic%20was%20their%20son.%20He%20said%20the%20person%20is%20now%20calling%20him%20and%20trying%20to%20cheat%20him.%20Investigation%20is%20on.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707589200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F49buttd8_delhi-boy-becomes-monk-_625x300_07_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fthe-monk-who-scammed-a-family-long-lost-son-turns-out-to-be-a-fraud-5033551%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20heart-warming%20tale%20of%20a%20mother's%20long-lost%20son%20returning%20as%20a%20monk%20after%2022%20years%20has%2C%20in%20less%20than%20a%20fortnight%2C%20devolved%20into%20a%20heart-rendin