of%20the%20nation%2C%C2%A0keeping%20in%20mind%20people's%20sentiment...%2037%20years%20after%20his%20death%2C%20a%20government%20thought%20of%20honouring%20him.%20If%20they%20are%20seeing%20something%20wrong%20with%20this%20and%20if%20they%20think%20there%20is%20a%20transaction%2C%20it%20shows%20their%20ideological%20decline.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20what%20went%20wrong%20with%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%2C%20he%20said%20it%20is%20an%20%26quot%3Binternal%20matter%26quot%3B%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20will%20explain%20later%20why%20he%20changed%20his%20stand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThose%20are%20internal%20matters%2C%20based%20on%20trust.%20Whatever%20discussions%20took%20place%20between%20me%20and%20Akhilesh%20ji%2C%20I%20will%20not%20discuss%20it%20outside...%20When%20our%20alliance%20is%20decided%20and%20announced%2C%20I%20will%20be%20able%20to%20tell%20why%20I%20changed%20my%20stand%20and%20the%20way%20ahead%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20his%20earlier%20remarks%20that%20he%20will%20not%20%26quot%3Bflip%20like%20a%20coin%26quot%3B%2C%20Singh%20said%20there%20should%20be%20an%20%26quot%3Bexpiry%20date%26quot%3B%20to%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20used%20to%20happen%20earlier%20as%20well%2C%20but%20earlier%20the%20records%20were%20not%20available%20all%20the%20time.%20In%20the%20times%20of%20internet%2C%20you%20can%20also%20see%20my%20statements%20from%2020%20years%20ago%20when%20I%20fought%20with%20the%20support%20of%20the%20BJP%20and%20became%20an%20MP%20from%20Mathura.%20There%20is%20an%20expiry%20date%20to%20statements%2C%20something%20was%20said%20during%20poll%20campaign...%20Amit%20Shah%20had%20said%20something%20about%20me%2C%20I%20said%20something%20to%20keep%20my%20people%20together.%20I%20did%20not%20intend%20to%20insult%20him%2C%20nor%20did%20he%20take%20it%20personally.%20Otherwise%2C%20would%20Chaudhary%20sahab%20get%20a%20Bharat%20Ratna%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am