ment%20on%20Saturday%20(February%2010)%20that%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20verdict%20on%20the%20Ram%20Janambhoomi%20showed%20India%E2%80%99s%20secularism%20to%20the%20world%20and%20that%20in%20no%20other%20country%20did%20the%20majority%20community%20have%20to%20fight%20such%20a%20long%20legal%20battle%20for%20its%20faith.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAddressing%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20during%20the%20discussion%20titled%20%E2%80%9CDiscussion%20on%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20historic%20Ram%20Temple%20and%20the%20Pran%20Pratishtha%E2%80%9D%2C%20Shah%20said%20that%20the%20Ram%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya%20had%20showed%20to%20the%20country%20that%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20fulfil%20the%20promises%20they%20make.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20itself%20has%20given%20an%20order%20through%20a%205-judge%20bench%2C%20how%20can%20you%20question%20it%3F%20If%20you%20like%20the%20order%20then%20accept%20the%20order%20and%20if%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20like%20the%20order%20you%20still%20will%20have%20to%20respect%20the%20court%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Supreme%20Court%20order%20has%20shown%20to%20the%20world%20India%E2%80%99s%20secular%20character.%20In%20no%20other%20country%20in%20the%20world%20did%20the%20majority%20community%20have%20to%20fight%20such%20a%20long%20legal%20battle%20for%20its%20faith.%20We%20have%20seen%20the%20way%2C%20and%20we%20have%20fought%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20and%20only%20after%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20judgement%20has%20a%20Ram%20Mandir%20been%20built.%20I%20want%20to%20reiterate%2C%20when%20everyone%20is%20celebrating%2C%20you%20should%20also%20welcome%20it%20and%20this%20is%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20the%20nation%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shah%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShah%20said%20that%20January%2022%20marked%20the%20end%20of%20a%20long%20struggle%20since%201528%20that%20has%20ended%20with%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20Ram%20Temple.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20date%20of%20January%2022%20marks%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20journey%20of%20great%20India.%20This%20day%20paves%20the%20way%20for%20Maa%20Bharti%20(mother%20India)%20to%20take%20us%20on%20the%20path%20of%20becoming%20Vishwaguru%20(world%20leader).%20It%20was%20a%20day%20that%20marked%20the%20hopes%2C%20aspirations%20and%20accomplishments%20of%20crores%20of%20devotees%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20mentioned%20it%20in%20our%20manifesto%2C%20they%20said%20it%20was%20only%20to%20win%20the%20elections%20and%20that%20the%20BJP%20keeps%20making%20promises%20like%20scrapping%20Article%20370%2C%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%2C%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20or%20Triple%20Talaq.%20However%2C%20they%20oppose%20us%20every%20time%20we%20fulfil%20our%20promises.%20The%20temple%20shows%20that%20the%20BJP%20and%20PM%20Modi%20fulfill%20all%20their%20promises%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShah%20said%20that%20during%20the%20consecration%20ceremony%2C%20no%20political%20slogans%20were%20raised%20and%20the%20message%20was%20one%20of%20unity.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20want%20to%20say%20with%20folded%20hands%20that%20accept%20the%20message%20of%20unity%20and%20move%20forward%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20interim%20budget%20session%20of%20parliament%20which%20began%20on%20January%2031%20was%20due%20to%20end%20on%20February%209%20but%20was%20extended%20by%20a%20day%20to%20Saturday%2C%20with%20both%20houses%20of%20parliament%20holding%20a%20discussion%20on%20the%20consecration%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya%20last%20month.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDuring%20the%20discussion%20Congress%20MP%20Gaurav%20Gogoi%20said%20that%20the%20party%20believes%20in%20secularism%20and%20that%20the%20treasury%20benches%20should%20leave%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20path%20of%20Nathuram%20Godse%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20believe%20in%20secularism%2C%20but%20not%20the%20western%20definition%20of%20secularism.%20India%20is%20a%20%3Cem%3Edharmik%20%3C%2Fem%3E(religious)%20country%20and%20we%20believe%20in%20sarva%20dharma%20sam%20bhava.%20We%20want%20to%20bind%20everyone.%20This%20is%20our%20culture%20and%20civilisation.%20I%20call%20upon%20the%20treasury%20benches%20to%20leave%20the%20path%20of%20Nathuram%20Godse%3B%20to%20not%20celebrate%20but%20condemn%20him.%20Ravana%20was%20killed%20by%20his%20arrogance.%20Your%20arrogance%20makes%20you%20blind%20to%20inflation%2C%20and%20problems%20in%20society%20%E2%80%93%20be%20it%20in%20Manipur%20or%20those%20faced%20by%20minorities.%20India%20is%20an%20ancient%20country%3B%20it%20was%20not%20born%20in%202014%20or%20on%20January%2022%2C%202024.%20Ram%20Lalla%20was%20always%20with%20us.%20Ram%20will%20be%20there%20when%20you%20lose%20too.%20Ram%20is%20in%20our%20hearts%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gogoi%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGogoi%20also%20asked%20the%20treasury%20benches%20about%20why%20hatred%20has%20been%20infused%20to%20chants%20like%20%E2%80%9CJai%20Shree%20Ram.%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWhy%20is%20there%20such%20bitterness%2C%20and%20hatred%20when%20they%20say%20Jai%20Shri%20Ram%3F%20If%20you%20hate%20people%20and%20spread%20hatred%2C%20and%20disturb%20others%E2%80%99%20religious%20practices%2C%20you%20cannot%20be%20a%20Ram%20Bhakt%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20India%20Majlis-e-Ittehadul%20Muslimeen%20(AIMIM)%20MP%20Asaduddin%20Owaisi%20said%20that%20the%20government%20should%20clarify%20whether%20it%20believes%20in%20one%20religion.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20want%20to%20ask%20if%20the%20Modi%20government%20is%20the%20government%20of%20a%20particular%20community%2C%20religion%20or%20the%20government%20of%20the%20entire%20country%3F%20Does%20the%20government%20of%20India%20have%20a%20religion%3F%20I%20believe%20that%20this%20country%20does%20not%20have%20a%20religion.%20Through%2022nd%20January%2C%20does%20this%20government%20want%20to%20give%20a%20message%20that%20one%20religion%20triumphed%20over%20the%20other%3F%20Does%20law%20allow%20this%3F%20What%20message%20do%20you%20give%20to%20the%2017%20crore%20Muslims%20in%20the%20country%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAmol%20Ramsingh%20Kolhe%20of%20the%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20(NCP)%20said%20that%20while%20the%20construction%20of%20Ram%20temple%20was%20historic%2C%20there%20should%20be%20%E2%80%9Cno%20politics%20over%20religion%20and%20religion%20should%20not%20be%20in%20politics.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20world%E2%80%99s%20history%20shows%20that%20religious%20fundamentalism%20is%20harmful%20while%20religious%20openness%20is%20constructive%20and%20that%20is%20what%20Hinduism%20shows%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20Shiv%20Sena%20MP%20Priyanka%20Chaturvedi%20said%20crediting%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20to%20only%20Modi%20is%20to%20%E2%80%9Cinsult%20those%20who%20fought%20for%20500%20years%20including%20those%20who%20fought%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707573276000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F11121926%2FScreenshot-2024-01-11-at-12.18.29-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fon-last-day-in-parliament-bjp-tries-to-draw-ram-temple-back-on-political-centre-stage%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amit%20Shah%2C%20who%20did%20not%20attend%20the%20pran%20pratishthan%20ceremony%2C%20spoke%20of%20the%20Ayodhya%20litigation%20in%20court.%20Congress'%20Gaurav%20Gogoi%20asked%20BJP%20to%20shed%20the%20%26quot%3Bpath%20of%20Nathuram%20Godse%26quot%3B%20and%20AIMIM's%20Asaduddin%20Owaisi%20asked%20if%20the%20government%20only%20favoured%20one%20particular%20faith.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fon-last-day-in-parliament-bjp-tries-to-draw-ram-temple-back-on-political-centre-stage%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20Peace%20Negotiations%20Between%20Russia%20and%20Ukraine%20Failed%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F20165942%2F51905521463_0600c20141_k.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20the%20Ukrainian%20war%20approaches%20its%20second%20anniversary%2C%20there%20is%20renewed%2C%20if%20rather%20limp%2C%20talk%20of%20a%20ceasefire%20followed%20by%20negotiations.%20The%20premise%20(and%20promise)%20is%20that%20since%20neither%20side%20can%20%E2%80%98win%E2%80%99%2C%20it%20makes%20sense%20to%20start%20making%20peace.%20Few%20now%20remember%20that%20the%20war%20almost%20ended%20before%20it%20got%20going.%20On%20February%2024%2C%202022%2C%20Russia%20launched%20ground%20and%20air%20attacks%20on%20Ukraine%20on%20four%20fronts.%20On%20February%2028%2C%202022%2C%20Russian%20and%20Ukrainian%20officials%20came%20together%20in%20Gomel%2C%20Belarus%20to%20start%20negotiating%20peace.%20Peace%20talks%20continued%20on%20and%20off%20for%20a%20month%20before%20being%20called%20off.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKnowledge%20of%20these%20talks%20has%20been%20steadily%20leaking%20out%20ever%20since%20Russian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%20waved%20a%20%E2%80%98peace%20agreement%E2%80%99%20before%20Russian%20TV%20cameras%20on%20June%2017%2C%202023%2C%20which%2C%20he%20said%2C%20Ukraine%20had%20%E2%80%98trashed%E2%80%99.%20It%20was%20a%20%E2%80%9CTreaty%20on%20permanent%20neutrality%20and%20security%20guarantees%20of%20Ukraine%E2%80%9D%20with%2018%20articles%20and%20an%20appendix%20dealing%20with%20%E2%80%98armed%20forces%20and%20other%20things%E2%80%99%20Putin%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELast%20month%2C%20Kremlin%20spokesperson%20Dmitri%20Peskov%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9CBritain%20had%20sunk%20chances%20of%20a%20peace%20deal%20in%202022%20by%20putting%20pressure%20of%20Kyiv%20to%20refuse%20a%20draft%20deal%E2%80%9D%20shortly%20after%20Russia%20sent%20troops%20into%20Ukraine.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20actually%20happened%20in%20February-March%202022%3F%20And%20what%20does%20it%20tell%20us%20about%20the%20prospects%20of%20peace%20today%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EThe%20negotiations%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERussia%20invaded%20Ukraine%20on%20February%2024%2C%202022%3B%20four%20days%20later%2C%20both%20sides%20started%20talking%20in%20Belarus.%20According%20to%20the%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2022%2F12%2F28%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fukraine-russia-peace-talks.html%5C%22%3E%20%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ENew%20York%20Times%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cb%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3EUkraine%20demanded%20Russia%20be%20held%20accountable%20for%20war%20atrocities%2C%20withdraw%20from%20all%20captured%20Ukraine%20territory%2C%20including%20Crimea%2C%20and%20pay%20reparations.%20Russia%20demanded%20Ukrainian%20recognition%20of%20its%20annexation%20of%20Crimea%20in%202014%2C%20permanent%20Ukrainian%20neutrality%2C%20and%20autonomy%20for%20the%20ethnic%20Russian%20provinces%20or%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eoblasts%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20eastern%20and%20south-eastern%20Ukraine.%20No%20progress%20was%20made%2C%20but%20both%20sides%20agreed%20to%20continue%20talking%2C%20this%20time%20with%20representatives%20of%20their%20foreign%20and%20defence%20ministries%2C%20and%20presidential%20administrations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter