20fiction.%20Although%20it%20may%20appear%20closer%20to%20reality%20than%20fiction.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20central%20committee%20for%20success%20(CCS)%E2%80%94a%20high-level%2C%20influential%20monitoring%20body%20set%20up%20by%20the%20Hon%E2%80%99ble%20prime%20minister%2C%20met%20on%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EFebruary%2010%20in%20a%20regular%20session%2C%20a%20monthly%20ritual%20to%20take%20stock%20of%20the%20changing%20political%20landscape.%20As%20per%20the%20protocol%2C%20the%20meeting%20was%20off%20the%20books%20%E2%80%93%20no%20record%2C%20no%20notes%2C%20no%20information%2C%20and%20of%20course%20no%20PIB%20press%20release%3B%20not%20even%2C%20an%20ANI%20report.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20was%20a%20sense%20of%20admiration%20and%20awe%20at%20the%20way%20the%20prime%20minister%20had%20moved%20on%20various%20fronts%20with%20dexterity%20and%20panache.%20While%20there%20was%20no%20particular%20jubilation%20over%20his%20two%20recent%20parliamentary%20performances%20%5Broutine%20and%20predictable%2C%20as%20one%20participant%20muttered%20inaudibly%5D%2C%20there%20was%20positive%20excitement%20over%20the%20imaginative%20use%20the%20prime%20minister%20has%20made%20of%20the%C2%A0%20%E2%80%9CBharat%20Ratna%E2%80%99%20awards%20to%20garner%20a%20few%2C%20petty%20political%20advantages.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Big%20Boss%20proxy%20revealed%20the%20thinking%20at%20the%20highest%20level%3A%20let%20editorial%20writers%20vent%20their%20disapproval%20at%20this%20%E2%80%9Ccheapening%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20award%20but%20anything%20and%20everything%20that%20helps%20in%20getting%20over%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20majority%20line%20will%20be%20pursued.%20He%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIf%20I%20can%20paraphrase%20the%20boss%E2%80%99s%20thought%20process%2C%20it%20goes%20like%20this%3A%C2%A0%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20not%20bothered%20with%20constitutional%20protocols%2C%20sanctity%20of%20traditions%20and%20all%20that%20%3Cem%3Ebakwas%3