al%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20did%20not%20give%20the%20founder%20of%20our%20party%20the%20highest%20honour%2C%20it%20will%20also%20endear%20us%20to%20the%20bhadralok%20constituency%20which%20still%20remains%20loyal%20to%20Mamta%20Banerjee.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBiju%20Patnaik%3A%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20shall%20be%20able%20to%20knock%20off%20Navin%20Patnaik%20from%20his%20smug%20love%20affair%20with%20the%20Oriya%20voter.%20We%20shall%20steal%20the%20father%20from%20the%20son%20and%20many%20more%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20from%20Orissa.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20CCS%20was%20given%20to%20understand%20that%20no%20one%20should%20be%20surprised%20if%20one%20Bharat%20Ratna%20a%20week%20was%20announced%20before%20the%20model%20code%20of%20conduct%20comes%20into%20play.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYet%20many%20CCS%20members%20were%20curious%20to%20know%20why%20so%20much%20trouble%20is%20being%20taken%20when%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20has%20already%20declared%20that%20the%20BJP%20would%20win%20more%20than%20370%20seats%20in%20the%20next%20Lok%20Sabha.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Big%20Boss%20Proxy%3A%20%E2%80%9CThat%20is%20where%20nobody%20has%20ever%20been%20able%20to%20de-code%20the%20sheer%20street-smartness%20of%20the%20Boss%E2%80%99%20grand%20strategy.%20You%20create%20this%20massive%20perception%2C%20with%20those%20silly%20Pavlovian%20dogs%20in%20the%20media%20echoing%20the%20inevitability%20of%20a%20Modi%20wave.%20They%20fall%20over%20one%20another%20in%20serenading%20this%20or%20that%20master-stroke%20by%20the%20prime%20minister.%20They%20openly%20permit%20themselves%20to%20say%20how%20clever%20and%20brilliant%20our%20man%20is%3B%20and%2C%20by%20the%20same%20token%2C%20they%20have%20good%20reason%20to%20find%20the%20opposition%20in%20a%20disarray.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CHere%20is%20the%20secret%20%5Bnot%20to%20be%20