20that%20no%20one%20wants%20to%20take%20a%20%3Cem%3Epanga%3C%2Fem%3E%20with%20a%20sure%20%E2%80%98winner%E2%80%99.%20And%20the%20cherry%20on%20the%20cake%20will%20be%20that%20the%20media%20will%20pat%20itself%20on%20the%20back%20for%20being%20so%20precise%20and%20accurate%20in%20predicting%20a%20Modi%20wave.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20CCS%20was%20once%20again%20in%20awe%20of%20the%20unending%20tricks%20the%20Big%20Boss%20has%20up%20his%20sleeve.%20They%20all%20felt%20it%20was%20time%20that%20he%20should%20give%20himself%20a%20Bharat%20Ratna.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EAtmanirbhar%20is%20the%20pen-name%20of%20an%20aspiring%20satirist%2C%20who%20irregularly%20contributes%20a%20column%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.thewire.in%2Fbyline%2Fatmanirbhar%5C%22%3EFrom%20the%20Vishwavguru%20Archives%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20believes%20that%20ridicule%20and%20humour%20are%20central%20to%20freedom%20to%20speech%20and%20expression.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707555730000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F02%2F11152259%2FIMG_0081.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fa-bharat-ratna-a-week-for-the-next-two-months%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22From%20the%20Vishwaguru%20Archives%3A%20Let%20editorial%20writers%20vent%20their%20disapproval%20at%20this%20%E2%80%9Ccheapening%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20award%2C%20there%20is%20positive%20excitement%20over%20the%20imaginative%20use%20the%20prime%20minister%20has%20made%20of%20the%C2%A0Bharat%20Ratna%20to%20garner%20a%20few%2C%20petty%20political%20advantages.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fa-bharat-ratna-a-week-for-the-next-two-months%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Russian%20'kamikaze'%20drone%20ignite