20Missionaries%20are%20converting%20schools%20and%20educational%20institutes%20into%20religious%20institutes.%20We%20will%20not%20allow%20it.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20group%20has%20warned%20of%20dire%20consequences%20if%20Christian%20schools%20fail%20to%20comply%20with%20the%20demand.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EArchbishop%20John%20Moolachira%20of%20Guwahati%20dismissed%20the%20allegations%20as%20baseless.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20aware%20of%20the%20threat%20and%20I%20do%20not%20understand%20why%20this%20is%20happening%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20UCA%20News%2C%20adding%20that%20legal%20means%20would%20be%20explored%20to%20address%20such%20open%20threats.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20response%20to%20the%20ultimatum%2C%20Christian%20leaders%20have%20advised%20priests%2C%20nuns%2C%20and%20brothers%20to%20wear%20civil%20Indian%20dresses%20on%20campuses%20as%20a%20precaution.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChristian%20leaders%20plan%20to%20approach%20Assam%20chief%20minister%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%2C%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%2C%20to%20address%20the%20threats%20posed%20to%20Christianity%20and%20missionary%20activities.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChristian%20leaders%20say%20threats%20to%20Christianity%20and%20missionary%20activities%20have%20increased%20in%20recent%20years%20in%20the%20entire%20northeast%20India%20region%20after%20Hindu%20groups%20began%20to%20push%20cultural%20nationalism.%20The%20Hindu%20groups%20have%20succeeded%20in%20portraying%20Christianity%20as%20a%20diabolical%20force%20to%20destroy%20Hindu%20native%20culture%20and%20to%20convert%20Hindus%20to%20Christianity%2C%20the%20UCA%20report%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20Assam%2C%20Christians%20make%20up%203.74%20percent%20of%20the%20population%2C%20exceeding%20the%20national%20average%20of%202.3%20percent.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20United%20Christian%20Forum%20(UCF)%2C%20a%20civil%20society%20organisation%20focused%20on%20Christian%20issues%2C%20had%20released%20a%20statement%20last%20year%20highlighting%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fdata-rise-in-attacks-on-christians-in-india-up-four-times-in-11-years-2012-2022%5C%22%3Ethe%20rise%20in%20attacks%20against%20the%20community%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20pointed%20out%20that%20there%20had%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fdata-rise-in-attacks-on-christians-in-india-up-four-times-in-11-years-2012-2022%5C%22%3E525%20attacks%20against%20Christians%20in%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%20just%20in%20the%20first%20eight%20months%20of%202023.%20The%20group%20had%20cautioned%20that%20if%20the%20trend%20were%20to%20continue%20then%202023%20would%20prove%20to%20be%20one%20of%20the%20most%20violent%20and%20difficult%20years%20the%20Christian%20community%20in%20India%20has%20ever%20seen%2C%20breaking%20the%20recent%20record%20set%20by%202022%2C%20and%202021%20before%20that.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20these%20incidents%20of%20violence%20are%20by%20mob%20violence%20led%20by%20so%20called%20vigilante%20groups%20of%20particular%20faith%20who%20are%20allegedly%20receiving%20support%20from%20people%20in%20power%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20organisation%20said%20in%20a%20press%20release.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707553720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F20233349%2FIMG_0509.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fassam-hindu-group-threatens-christian-schools-to-remove-religious-symbols-or-face-dire-outcome%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20ultimatum%20issued%20by%20one%20Kutumba%20Surakshya%20Parishad%20includes%20removal%20of%20idols%20and%20photographs%20of%20Jesus%20and%20Mary%20as%20well%20as%20churches%20located%20on%20school%20complexes.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22