%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F10112435%2Frs2.jpg%201039w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F10112435%2Frs2-300x113.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F10112435%2Frs2-1024x387.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-696475%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22393%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20reason%20for%20deaths%20of%20cheetahs%20as%20submitted%20by%20Union%20environment%20minister%20Bhupender%20Yadav%20on%20February%208.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20instance%2C%20the%20National%20Tiger%20Conservation%20Authority%20%E2%80%93%20which%20is%20implementing%20Project%20Cheetah%20%E2%80%93%20had%20issued%20a%20statement%20on%20July%2016%20last%20year%20saying%20that%20all%20cheetah%20deaths%20occurred%20due%20to%20%E2%80%9Cnatural%20causes%E2%80%9D%20and%20that%20any%20reports%20attributing%20the%20deaths%20to%20other%20reasons%20are%20%E2%80%9Cspeculation%20and%20hearsay%20and%20not%20based%20on%20any%20scientific%20evidence%E2%80%9D.%20This%20came%20a%20day%20after%20two%20experts%20on%20the%20Cheetah%20Project%20Steering%20Committee%20had%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fproject-cheetah-deaths-radio-collar-infections%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Etold%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(on%20July%2015%20last%20year)%20that%20the%20deaths%20of%20Tejas%20and%20Suraj%20were%20caused%20by%20septicaemia%2C%20an%20infection%20of%20the%20bloodstream%2C%20brought%20on%20by%20wounds%20caused%20by%20the%20combined%20effects%20of%20abrasion%20of%20radio%20collars%20fitted%20on%20their%20necks%20and%20moisture%20accumulated%20under%20the%20collars.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20of%20the%20experts%20also%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fthree-more-cheetahs-in-kuno-have-neck-infections%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Etold%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20Suraj%E2%80%99s%20death%20was%20%E2%80%9Cpotentially%20avoidable%E2%80%9D%20and%20that%20authorities%20lost%20%E2%80%9Ca%20full%20day%E2%80%9D%20in%20taking%20action%20while%20waiting%20for%20the%20post-mortem%20report%20of%20Tejas%2C%20the%20first%20cheetah%20to%20die%20of%20a%20neck%20wound%20on%20July%2011.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20August%202%2C%20a%20press%20note%20released%20by%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20forest%20department%20said%20that%20a%20monitoring%20team%20found%20Dhatri%2C%20a%20female%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fninth-cheetah-dies-in-kuno-national-park%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edead%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20the%20wild%20in%20Kuno%20that%20morning.%20The%20animal%2C%20which%20authorities%20were%20trying%20to%20capture%20from%20the%20wild%20after%20the%20deaths%20of%20Tejas%20and%20Surya%2C%20was%20then%20the%20sixth%20adult%20to%20die.%20In%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FCCFCheetah%2Fstatus%2F1687116755548995584%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eseries%20of%20tweets%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20August%203%2C%20the%20Cheetah%20Conservation%20Fund%20(CCF)%20which%20has%20assisted%20Project%20Cheetah%2C%20said%20that%20a%20post-mortem%20revealed%20that%20Dhatri%20died%20due%20to%20myiasis%2C%20or%20infection%20caused%20by%20fly%20larvae%20(maggots).%20As%20per%20Yadav%E2%80%99s%20latest%20list%2C%20Dhatri%20died%20of%20septicemia.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20seventh%20death%20%E2%80%94%20and%20most%20recent%20so%20far%20%E2%80%94%20is%20that%20of%20Shaurya%2C%20a%20male%20from%20Namibia%2C%20on%20January%2016.%20Yadav%2C%20in%20his%20recent%20list%2C%20has%20also%20submitted%20to%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20that%20Shaurya%20too%20died%20of%20septicemia.%20The%20animal%2C%20housed%20in%20an%20enclosure%2C%20was%20treated%20for%20%E2%80%9Cweakness%E2%80%9D%20after%20it%20displayed%20a%20%E2%80%9Cstaggering%20gait%E2%80%9D%2C%20officials%20had%20said.%20However%2C%20the%20animal%20died%20despite%20treatment.%20Officials%20had%20said%20the%20cause%20of%20death%20could%20be%20ascertained%20only%20once%20the%20detailed%20post-mortem%20results%20%E2%80%93%20which%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20announced%20by%20the%20Ministry%20or%20the%20NTCA%20%E2%80%93%20came%20in.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPer%20Yadav%E2%80%99s%20reply%3A%20%E2%80%9CTo%20ensure%20conservation%20and%20protection%20of%20Cheetahs%20in%20India%2C%20actions%20are%20taken%20as%20per%20scientific%20action%20plan%20prepared%20with%20inputs%20of%20leading%20Cheetah%20experts%20including%20biologists%2C%20ecologists%2C%20conservationists%20and%20managers.%20A%20Cheetah%20Project%20Steering%20Committee%20has%20been%20constituted%20to%20review%20progress%2C%20monitor%20and%20advise%20on%20the%20Cheetah%20introduction%20in%20consultation%20with%20international%20cheetah%20experts%2C%20as%20and%20when%20required.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20per%20the%20Action%20Plan%20for%20the%20introduction%20of%20Cheetah%2C%2012-14%20individuals%20per%20year%20are%20proposed%20to%20be%20brought%20from%20South%20Africa%20and%20Namibia%20or%20other%20African%20countries%20during%20the%20next%20five%20years%2C%20depending%20upon%20the%20availability%20of%20animals%20and%20status%20of%20introduced%20cheetahs%2C%20Yadav%20said%20in%20his%20response%20to%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha.%20His%20reply%20also%20mentioned%20that%20actions%20are%20being%20taken%20to%20introduce%20cheetahs%20into%20Gandhi%20Sagar%20Wildlife%20Sanctuary.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707544565000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F01124706%2FFr_KjcBXoAEm2rW.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fsepticemia-caused-deaths-of-four-cheetahs-union-environment-minister%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Adult%20male%20Shaurya%20that%20died%20on%20January%2016%20is%20the%20fourth%20cheetah%20to%20die%20due%20to%20septicemia%2C%20Minister%20Bhupender%20Yadav%20told%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha.%20%C2%A0%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fsepticemia-caused-deaths-of-four-cheetahs-union-environment-minister%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22EPFO%20fixes%208.25%25%20interest%20rate%20on%20employees'%20provident%20fund%20for%202023-24%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707543898000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2020-03%2F26%2Ffull%2F1585228707-6391.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Ffinance%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fepfo-fixes-8-25-interest-rate-on-employees-provident-fund-for-2023-24-124021000343_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Retirement%20fund%20body%20EPFO%20on%20Saturday%20fixed%20a%20three-year%20high%20interest%20rate%20of%208.25%25%20on%20employees'%20provident%20fund%20(EPF)%20deposits%20for%202023-24%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Ffinance%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fepfo-fixes-8-25-interest-rate-on-employees-provident-fund-for-2023-24-124021000343_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Ffinance%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fepfo-fixes-8-25-interest-rate-on-employees-provident-fund-for-2023-24-124021000343_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Ffinance%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fepfo-fixes-8-25-interest-rate-on-employees-provident-fund-for-2023-24-124021000343_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Elon%20Musk's%20firm%20Neuralink%20ditches%20Delaware%2C%20reincorporates%20in%20Nevada%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707528827000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-02%2F10%2Ffull%2F1707528716-0174.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fworld-news%2Felon-musk-s-firm-neuralink-ditches-delaware-reincorporates-in-nevada-124021000067_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Neuralink%20isn't%20the%20first%20business%20Musk%20has%20reincorporated%20outside%20of%20Delaware%20and%20may%20not%20be%20the%20last%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fworld-news%2Felon-musk-s-firm-neuralink-ditches-delaware-reincorporates-in-nevada-124021000067_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fworld-news%2Felon-musk-s-firm-neuralink-ditches-delaware-reincorporates-in-nevada-124021000067_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fworld-news%2Felon-musk-s-firm-neuralink-ditches-delaware-reincorporates-in-nevada-124021000067_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Fiscal%20Injustice'%20Powers%20a%20New%20Axis%20of%20Protest%20Against%20Modi%20Govt%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F09211831%2FFotoJet-3.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20simmering%20fault%20line%20between%20BJP-led%20Centre%20and%20non-BJP%20governments%20in%20states%20came%20to%20a%20boil%20this%20week.%20On%20Wednesday%2C%20chief%20minister%20Siddaramaiah%20and%20his%20deputy%20D.K.%20Shivakumar%20led%20an%20agitation%20against%20the%20Centre%E2%80%99s%20alleged%20%E2%80%9Cfinancial%20injustice%E2%80%9D%20towards%20Karnataka.%20A%20day%20later%2C%20the%20Kerala%20government%20led%20by%20chief%20minister%20Pinarayi%20Vijayan%20staged%20a%20similar%20protest%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20national%20capital.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EVijayan%20was%20also%20accompanied%20by%20Delhi%20chief%20minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%2C%20his%20Punjab%20counterpart%20Bhagwant%20Mann%2C%20and%20DMK%20minister%20P.%20Thiagarajan.%20The%20chief%20ministers%20of%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20and%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20YSR%20Jagan%20Mohan%20Reddy%20and%20M.K.Stalin%2C%20also%20protested%20against%20the%20unfair%20devolution%20of%20taxes%20to%20states%20that%20have%20contributed%20the%20most%20to%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20exchequer.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20the%20first%20time%20that%20all%20these%20states%20have%20taken%20to%20popular%20protests%20on%20these%20issues%2C%20moving%20the%20question%20of%20partisanship%20over%20resources%20out%20of%20discussion%20rooms.%20The%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi-led%20Telangana%20government%20had%20also%20agitated%20over%20the%20issue%20in%202023.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EThe%20argument%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBoth%20Karnataka%20and%20Kerala%20governments%20are%20demanding%20that%20their%20share%20in%20the%20devolution%20of%20taxes%20to%20states%20by%20the%20Union%20finance%20ministry%20should%20be%20greater%20than%20what%20they%20currently%20receive%2C%20given%20their%20share%20of%20contribution%20to%20the%20exchequer%20is%20also%20greater%20than%20most%20other%20states%20who%20receive%20a%20better%20share.%20Moreover%2C%20they%20have%20said%20that%20even%20the%20mandated%20devolution%20of%20taxes%20to%20Karnataka%20and%20Kerala%20has%20not%20been%20fulfilled%20by%20the%20Union%20finance%20ministry%2C%20and%20has%20created%20a%20backlog%20in%20the%20development%20goals%20of%20the%20states.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20are%20allied%20issues%2C%20too.%20The%20Karnataka%20government%20alleged%20that%20the%20Centre%20has%20not%20released%20special%20grants%20worth%20Rs%205495%20crores%2C%20as%20recommended%20by%20the%2015th%20Finance%20Commission%2C%20and%20also%20denied%20the%20promised%20grant%20of%20around%20Rs%206000%20crores%20for%20drought-hit%20Karnataka%20which%20it%20could%20have%20used%20for%20infrastructure%20development%20of%20water%20bodies%20and%20irrigation%20projects.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Finance%20Commission%20is%20the%20Constitutional%20body%20to%20devise%20a%20formula%20for%20devolution%20of%20taxes%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20demographic%20performance%2C%20demographic%20performance%2C%20area%2C%20income%20distance%2C%20tax%20and%20fiscal%20efforts%2C%20forest%20cover%20and%20so%20on.%20The%20highest%20weightage%20is%20given%20to%20the%20population%20of%20states%2C%20which%20has%20meant%20that%20states%20which%20have%20been%20able%20to%20contain%20their%20population%20spiral%20eventually%20end%20up%20at%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20ladder%20of%20beneficiaries.%20The%20southern%20states%20have%20historically%20done%20better%20than%20north%20Indian%20states%20in%20almost%20all%20the%20criteria%20of%20development%20indices%20and%20emerged%20as%20the%20highest%20contributors%20of%20taxes%20to%20the%20exchequer.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYet%2C%20their%20share%20in%20the%20devolution%20of%20taxes%20is%20the%20least.%20The%20charts%20shared%20on%20X%20by%20DMK%E2%80%99s%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20P.Wilson%20post%20on%20X%20gives%20a%20fair%20idea%20of%20the%20devolution%20of%20taxes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EPlease%20find%20the%20flow%20chart%20provided%20below%20to%20assist%20with%20better%20understanding.%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FBJPLootingOurTax%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23BJPLootingOurTax%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F089YuHP7O3%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F089YuHP7O3%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20P.%20Wilson%20(%40PWilsonDMK)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FPWilsonDMK%2Fstatus%2F1755566669630509322%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%208%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20finance%20commission%E2%80%99s%20formula%20has%20dis-incentivised%20states%20to%20excel%2C%20as%20that%20may%20also%20result%20in%20a%20dramatic%20slashing%20of%20their%20share%20in%20tax%20revenues.%20For%20instance%2C%20if%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EMaharashtra%20shares%20Rs%201%20with%20the%20Centre%2C%20it%20is%20eligible%20to%20get%20back%20only%20Rs%200.08%20paise.%20Similarly%2C%20Karnataka%20will%20get%20back%20Rs%200.15%20paise%2C%20while%20Gujarat%20will%20receive%20Rs%200.08%20paise%20and%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Rs%200.29%20paise.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20states%20whose%20governments%20have%20performed%20poorly%20to%20control%20their%20population%20and%20made%20least%20tax%20and%20fiscal%20effort%20get%20the%20maximum%20share%20of%20tax%20revenues.%20Thus%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20gets%20Rs%202.73%20for%20every%20rupee%20it%20shares%20with%20the%20Centre%2C%20while%20Bihar%20gets%20Rs%207.06.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20the%20southern%20states%20have%20performed%20better%20than%20most%20others%20on%20all%20fronts%2C%20while%20in%20the%20north%20of%20the%20Vindhyas%2C%20only%20Maharashtra%2C%20Gujarat%2C%20and%20Haryana%20match%20up%20to%20them.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20anomaly%20stands%20to%20only%20deepen%20with%20subsequent%20census%20exercises%2C%20and%20is%20crying%20out%20to%20be%20addressed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%2014th%20Finance%20Commission%20increased%20the%20vertical%20devolution%20of%20taxes%20to%20states%20to%2042%25%2C%20while%20the%2015th%2C%20currently%20in%20action%2C%20decreased%20it%20by%201%25%20to%2041%25%20However%2C%20the%20subsequent%20horizontal%20devolution%20is%20where%20states%20like%20Maharashtra%20and%20Karnataka%2C%20which%20are%20at%20the%20top%20of%20the%20pyramid%20as%20far%20as%20their%20contribution%20to%20the%20central%20pool%20is%20concerned%2C%20believe%20that%20they%20are%20getting%20a%20poor%20deal.%20To%20placate%20states%20which%20have%20performed%20historically%20well%2C%20the%2015th%20Finance%20Commission%20recommended%20special%20grants%2C%20which%20the%20Karnataka%20government%20said%20to%20have%20not%20received%2C%20and%20termed%20it%20as%20Centre%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cinjustice%E2%80%9D%20towards%20non-BJP%20states.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20BJP-led%20Centre%2C%20however%2C%20has%20denied%20all%20charges.%20The%20Union%20finance%20minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20said%20that%20her%20ministry%20has%20processed%20all%20dues%2C%20according%20to%20the%20rules%20of%20the%2015th%20Finance%20Commission%2C%20and%20asked%20the%20protesting%20governments%20to%20appeal%20to%20the%20Finance%20Commission%20instead%20of%20demonstrating%20against%20the%20Centre.%20But%20she%20remained%20silent%20on%20the%20question%20of%20special%20grants.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20BJP%20machinery%20has%20gone%20ahead%20to%20canvas%20that%20the%20non-BJP%20governments%20are%20attempting%20to%20divide%20the%20country%20along%20North-South%20lines%20and%20that%20the%20protests%20advocate%20separatism%20and%20even%20a%20split%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChief%20minister%20Siddaramaiah%20vehemently%20denied%20the%20accusation%20and%20said%20that%20India%20is%20a%20united%20country%2C%20but%20argued%20that%20Karnataka%20has%20continued%20to%20get%20a%20poor%20deal%20over%20the%20years.%20He%20said%20that%20the%20Karnataka%20government%20was%20promised%20a%20drought%20relief%20package%20by%20both%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20which%20has%20still%20not%20been%20finalised%2C%20despite%20the%20fact%20that%20223%20of%20the%20236%20taluks%20of%20the%20state%20are%20reeling%20under%20conditions%20of%20a%20severe%20drought.%20He%20said%20that%20the%20state%20government%20is%20demanding%20its%20just%20GST%20dues%20and%20special%20grants%20that%20have%20still%20not%20been%20released%20by%20the%20Centre%2C%20while%20also%20appealing%20to%20the%2016th%20Finance%20Commission%20of%20fixing%20a%20more%20fair%20deal%20for%20states%20which%20are%20taking%20the%20effort%20to%20improve%20conditions%20in%20the%20states.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20also%20said%20that%20the%2014th%20Finance%20Commission%20had%20fixed%20the%20share%20of%20taxes%20for%20Karnataka%20at%204.71%25%2C%20while%20the%2015th%20decreased%20it%20further%20to%203.65%25%2C%20representing%20a%20speculative%20loss%20of%20around%201.87%20lakh%20crores.%20%E2%80%9CPut%20together%2C%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20losses%20amount%20to%20around%20Rs%2062%2C098%20crore.%20Should%20we%20keep%20quiet%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20asked%2C%20adding%20that%20his%20protest%20was%20for%20Karnataka%20and%20its%20people%2C%20and%20that%20he%20had%20also%20invited%20the%20BJP%2C%20and%20its%20Karnataka%20leaders%20like%20Tejaswi%20Surya%2C%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%2C%20Pratap%20Simha%20and%20others%20to%20join%20the%20cause.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20appealed%20to%20the%2016th%20Finance%20Commission%20to%20decide%20states%E2%80%99%20share%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20the%201971%20Census%20to%20prevent%20such%20%E2%80%9Cinjustice%E2%80%9D%20towards%20Karnataka%20which%20has%20controlled%20its%20population%20through%20better%20implementation%20of%20birth%20control%20and%20economic%20parity%20measures%20over%20the%20years.%20Why%20should%20we%20be%20penalised%20for%20doing%20our%20work%20sincerely%2C%20he%20asked.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESimilarly%2C%20the%20Kerala%20government%20also%20alleged%20that%20it%20has%20not%20received%20dues%20worth%20Rs%2057%2C400%20crores%20in%20the%20current%20fiscal.%20Citing%20figures%20from%20a%20RBI%20report%2C%20it%20said%20that%20the%20Centre%20has%20continuously%20not%20met%20the%20requirements%20of%20even%20the%20%E2%80%9Cunjust%E2%80%9D%20devolution%20of%20taxes%20to%20opposition-ruled%20states.%20It%20said%20that%20it%20was%20denied%20Rs%2012%2C000%20crore%20this%20year%20scheduled%20to%20have%20come%20from%20GST%20compensation%20from%20June%202022.%C2%A0%20Chief%20minister%20Vijayan%20said%20that%20while%20Kerala%20received%203.87%25%20in%20the%20devolution%20of%20taxes%20during%20the%20period%20of%2010th%20finance%20commission%2C%20it%20came%20down%20to%202.5%25%20in%20the%2014th%20and%201.925%25%20in%20the%2015th%20finance%20commission%2C%20leading%20to%20huge%20losses%20for%20the%20state%20every%20subsequent%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20grieving%20states%20have%20complained%20about%20the%20Centre%20releasing%20only%20an%20average%20of%20only%2035%25%20as%20share%20to%20the%20states%2C%20as%20opposed%20to%20the%20mandated%2041%25%20recommended%20by%20the%2015th%20finance%20commission.%20Moreover%2C%20they%20said%20that%20the%20special%20grants%20as%20capital%20expenditure%20and%20capacity%20of%20states%20to%20borrow%20have%20also%20taken%20a%20hit%20because%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Cunfair%E2%80%9D%20devolution%20process.%20The%20anomalies%20in%20the%20promised%20GST%20compensation%20and%20failure%20to%20disburse%20the%20recommended%20special%20grants%20by%20the%20Centre%20to%20states%20have%20only%20escalated%20anger%20among%20opposition%20parties.%20They%20also%20believe%20that%20the%20share%20of%20tax%20revenue%20collected%20as%20%E2%80%9Ccess%E2%80%9D%20or%20%E2%80%9Csurcharge%E2%80%9D%20has%20grown%20dramatically%20during%20the%20Modi%20regime%2C%20from%2010%25%20during%20the%20UPA%20era%20to%20over%2026%25%20now%2C%20but%20is%20not%20shared%20with%20the%20states.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EAsking%20for%20their%20due%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20charge%20that%20the%20opposition-ruled%20states%20are%20trying%20to%20balkanise%20India%20lacks%20merit%20against%20such%20a%20backdrop.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20states%20like%20the%20BJP-ruled%20Gujarat%20and%20Haryana%20face%20the%20same%20problem%20and%20have%20raised%20their%20voices%20from%20time%20to%20time.%20Given%20the%20criteria%20of%20devolution%20and%20future%20census%20exercises%2C%20the%20gap%20between%20states%20like%20Maharashtra%2C%20Karnataka%20and%20poorly-performing%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20Bihar%2C%20which%20receive%20the%20highest%20share%20of%20taxes%20despite%20contributing%20the%20least%2C%20may%20only%20increase.%20This%20may%20lead%20to%20further%20escalation%20of%20the%20problem.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEconomists%20have%20long%20debated%20the%20issue.%20While%20some%20believe%20that%20the%20weightage%20of%20population%20could%20be%20decreased%20to%20prevent%20future%20fights%20between%20states%20and%20the%20Centre%2C%20some%20say%20that%20the%20devolution%20formula%20could%20be%20done%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20one%20of%20the%20pre-2011%20census%20data.%20Many%20others%20believe%20that%20a%20variable%20component%20could%20be%20introduced%20that%20takes%20into%20account%20the%20efforts%20made%20by%20states%20to%20close%20the%20huge%20gap%20between%20states%2C%20like%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20Bihar%2C%20and%20given%20more%20weightage%20in%20the%20devolution%20of%20taxes.%20They%20say%20that%20if%20the%20effort%20by%20states%20is%20not%20visible%2C%20then%20the%20whole%20purpose%20of%20supporting%20poor%20states%20to%20bring%20them%20at%20par%20with%20those%20with%20a%20good%20track%20record%20is%20defeated.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20tussle%20over%20%E2%80%9Cfiscal%20injustice%E2%80%9D%20has%20already%20begun%20to%20intensify%20the%20politics%20around%20it.%20This%20has%20made%20the%20Modi%20government%20uncomfortable%20as%20it%20is%20an%20agenda%20set%20by%20the%20opposition%2C%20that%20Modi%20knows%20will%20divert%20from%20is