ep%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20chair%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F331893%2Fmental-health-care-therapy-counselling-affordable-startups-india-online%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaffordable%20and%20cheap.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20point%20in%20making%20a%20product%20that%20the%20masses%20can%E2%80%99t%20afford.%20It%20defeats%20the%20entire%20sustainability%20angle%20behind%20the%20product%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20%E2%80%9CGujarat%20government%20has%20also%20released%20a%20lot%20of%20schemes%20for%20the%20farmers%20to%20encourage%20them%20to%20grow%20the%20plant%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20the%20cost%20of%20funding%20the%20project%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20did%20it%20out%20of%20my%20own%20pocket.%20I%20knew%20if%20I%20had%20gone%20out%20looking%20for%20funding%20then%20this%20would%20not%20have%20happened.%20Investors%20would%20lack%20confidence%20in%20the%20idea%20since%20it%20was%20new%20back%20then%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20Ankit%20nearly%20two%20years%20to%20complete%20the%20design%20and%20make%20the%20chair.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%202023%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20go%20ahead%20and%20get%20the%20chair%20patented.%20The%20main%20reason%20behind%20it%20was%20to%20showcase%20the%20potential%20of%20native%20bamboo%20species%20to%20the%20world.%20Once%20my%20design%20got%20patented%2C%20it%20generated%20a%20conversation%20among%20people%20about%20the%20potential%20of%20bamboo%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fabcf-9-1707399987.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20chair%20can%20endure%20150%20kgs%20of%20weight%20and%20can%20last%20more%20than%2020%20years.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fabcf-9-1707399987.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fabcf-9-1707399987-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fabcf-9-1707399987-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fabcf-9-1707399987-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fabcf-9-1707399987-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-341211%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20chair%20can%20endure%20150%20kg%20of%20weight%20and%20can%20last%20more%20than%2020%20years.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20the%20chair%2C%20Ankit%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20polish%20on%20the%20chair%20is%20done%20using%20natural%20oils.%20It%20can%20endure%20weights%20of%20more%20than%20150%20kg%2C%20and%20the%20furniture%20has%20also%20been%20treated%20to%20protect%20against%20any%20kind%20of%20insects.%20The%20life%20of%20the%20chair%20is%20up%20to%2020%20years%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnkit%20does%20not%20want%20to%20commercialise%20the%20chair.%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99ve%20received%20numerous%20inquiries%20about%20whether%20I%20am%20selling%20these%20chairs.%20However%2C%20my%20goal%20is%20not%20profit%20or%20loss.%20My%20aim%20is%20to%20raise%20awareness%20and%20provide%20training%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCurrently%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20working%20on%20a%20proposal%20to%20present%20to%20my%20university%20to%20initiate%20a%20program%20where%20individuals%20can%20come%20and%20learn%20how%20to%20make%20chairs%20and%20collaborate%20with%20me%20to%20create%20more%20furniture.%20This%20approach%20will%20allow%20me%20to%20train%20craftsmen%20in%20producing%20sustainable%20yet%20modern%20f