experience%20you%20give.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIntrigued%20at%20how%20this%20would%20work%2C%20Chotaram%20agreed.%20In%20a%20matter%20of%20minutes%2C%20the%20guest%20had%20registered%20the%20home%20on%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F273684%2Fbest-ecofriendly-homestay-munnar-book-treehouse%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etravel%20website%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20created%20an%20email%20address%20for%20Chhotaram%20through%20which%20he%20could%20access%20bookings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThus%20was%20born%20the%20Chhotaram%20Prajapat%20Homestay.%20%E2%80%9CI%20came%20up%20with%20the%20name%20on%20the%20spur%20of%20the%20moment.%20I%20said%20%E2%80%98name%20it%20after%20me%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20paying%20Rs%20700%20to%20a%20local%20cyber%20cafe%20to%20access%20the%20internet%20for%20bookings%20and%20buying%20a%20computer%20%E2%80%9Cthat%20took%20two%20hours%20to%20reply%20to%20an%20email%E2%80%9D%20to%20now%20accepting%20bookings%20at%20the%20click%20of%20a%20button%2C%20Chhotaram%20has%20come%20a%20long%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20538px)%20100vw%2C%20538px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-01-13-at-6.30.23-AM-1707396796.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22538%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20food%20at%20the%20homestay%20includes%20Dal%20Bati%20Churma%2C%20which%20has%20masala%20bati%2C%20makki%20ki%20bati%2C%20and%20thirki%20dal%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-01-13-at-6.30.23-AM-1707396796.jpeg%20538w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-01-13-at-6.30.23-AM-1707396796-300x251.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024