20But%20having%20crossed%20the%20age%20of%2035%20at%20that%20time%2C%20she%20decided%20that%20it%20was%20now%20or%20never.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20did%20have%20a%20worry%20at%20the%20back%20of%20my%20mind%20about%20what%20would%20happen%20if%20something%20were%20to%20happen%20to%20me.%20What%20would%20happen%20if%20the%20decision%20I%20took%20was%20the%20wrong%20one%3F%20People%20cautioned%20me%20against%20it%2C%20saying%20what%20if%20something%20happens%20to%20you%20on%20the%20trip%3F%20But%20I%20had%20decided%20that%20the%20trip%20was%20mandatory%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20adds%20that%20her%20sons%20were%20very%20supportive%20of%20her%20decision%20and%20the%20reason%20she%20could%20take%20this%20decision%20was%20the%20fact%20that%20they%20could%20manage%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20her%20first%20long%20biking%20trip%2C%C2%A0%20she%20went%20to%20Leh%20Ladakh%20for%2010%20days.%20She%20recounts%20that%20it%20was%20a%20challenge%2C%20but%20both%20mother%20and%20son%20learnt%20to%20manage%20without%20one%20other%20over%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20first%2C%20a%20shiver%20would%20run%20down%20my%20spine%20whenever%20I%20got%20a%20call%20from%20home.%20I%20would%20worry%20if%20Vedansh%20was%20doing%20okay.%20It%20was%20difficult%20for%20both%20of%20us.%20But%20after%20overcoming%20the%20initial%20hiccups%2C%20he%20adjusted%20very%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeing%20away%20from%20each%20other%20for%20such%20a%20long%20time%20was%20a%20first%20for%20both%20mother%20and%20son.%20It%E2%80%99s%20not%20all%20hunky%20dory%2C%20adds%20the%20mother.%20There%20were%20teething%20troubles%20initially%2C%20but%20they%20both%20got%20used%20to%20it%20over%20time%2C%20and%20when%20Moushmi%20came%20back%20with%20a%20certificate%20for%20completing%20the%20trip%2C%20Vedansh%20was%20very%20happy%20and%20proud%20of%20his%20%E2%80%98mumma%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20Vedansh%20got%20the%20