n%20her%20homestay%20in%20April%202022.%20%E2%80%9CWithin%20three%20months%2C%20we%20were%20ready%20to%20welcome%20our%20first%20guests%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%20with%20a%20smile.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20Afsana%20Homestay%20opened%20its%20doors%2C%20they%20have%20served%20over%20300%20guests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECreating%20her%20grandma%E2%80%99s%20magic%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20homestay%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20three%20categories%20of%20rooms%20at%20the%20property.%20We%20avoid%20taking%20guests%20who%20have%20kids%20below%208%20years%20because%20the%20walk%20up%20to%20the%20homestay%20might%20be%20too%20much%20for%20the%20little%20ones.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20property%20has%20private%20rooms%20with%20attached%20washrooms.%20The%20prices%20range%20between%20Rs%202%2C000%20to%203%2C000%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20season.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20also%20have%20private%20rooms%20with%20a%20shared%20washroom.%20The%20prices%20range%20from%20Rs%201%2C000%20to%202%2C000%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfsana%20also%20has%20a%20room%20perfect%20for%20backpackers%20and%20travellers%20on%20a%20budget.%20%E2%80%9CThese%20shared%20rooms%20provide%20an%20economical%20option%20at%20600%20rupees%20per%20bed.%20Washrooms%20are%20shared%20among%20guests%20in%20this%20category%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20experiences%20she%20provides%20in%20her%20homestay%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20provide%20a%20purely%20simple%20Himachali%20food%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F337937%2Fbest-budget-homestay-in-uttarakhand-the-nanda-stone-mukteshwar-by-ashish-verma%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexperience%20at%20our%20homestay.%20%3C%2Fa%3EOur%20caretaker%20and%20old%20cook%20from%20back%20home%20joined%20me%20with%20the%20operations%20of%20the%20homestay%20and%20cooked%20these%20delicious%20meals.%20We%20use%20our%20mother%E2%80%99s%20recipes%20for%20making%20the%20traditional%20dish%2C%20%3Cem%3ESiddu%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20served%20to%20our%20guests.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20the%20raw%20materials%20are%20usually%20sourced%20from%20her%20home%20farm.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20walnuts%20for%20the%20%3Cem%3Esiddu%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20ghee%20for%20the%20food%2C%20the%20veggies%20and%20milk%20are%20all%20sourced%20from%20my%20own%20farm%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fabcf-5-1707226745.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20homestay%20offers%20homecooked%20authentic%20Himachali%20food.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fabcf-5-1707226745.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fabcf-5-1707226745-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fabcf-5-1707226745-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fabcf-5-1707226745-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fabcf-5-1707226745-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-340929%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20homestay%20offers%20home-cooked%20authentic%20Himachali%20food.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20the%20activities%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20offer%20four%20to%20five%20activities%20as%20part%20of%20our%20package.%20Guests%20can%20enjoy%20a%20guided%20tour%20of%20the%20forest%20park%2C%20included%20in%20the%20package%2C%20during%20the%20morning%20or%20evening.%20We%20also%20take%20them%20to%20a%20secluded%